	   <tr><td colspan=2>At lvl 20, shaman make good healer, however at higher lvl most groups want a cleric to heal.&nbsp;&nbsp;In these groups a shaman's role is more buff and debuff, your slow line of spells being the most important debuff.  <br>I wonder too, if you didn't misqote the cost of the drakeal icegrinder,last I herd is was 2000pp.  Or were you talking about the sledgehammer?  if so you got the stats wrong.  <br>Yes shaman play the role of healler in some group even at high lvl.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
